Functional Requirements:

Theatre Partners (B2B):
        Onboard theatres with details (location, seating capacity, pricing, etc.).
        Manage movie schedules and seat availability.

End Customers (B2C):
        Browse movies by city, language, and genre.
        View theatre details and seating availability.
        Book tickets and receive confirmation.


Non-Functional Requirements:

Scalability: Handle high traffic during popular movie releases.

Performance: Ensure low latency for seat booking and browsing.

Reliability: Avoid double booking through ACID-compliant transactions.

Security: Secure customer and partner data; ensure safe payment transactions.

